description: Star quarterback Josh Weston gets kidnapped by a sinister group of Latino frat boys. Fernando Montana, Diego Alvarez, Jonathan Diaz, Victor Rios, Rocky Castro, Nick Thomas, Vin Nolan, Mario Ortiz, Alex Leon, and Rick Gonzales all have their way with the milky-white stud's unstoppable ass in one of the most talked about gang-bang scene ever captured on film.
title: Quarterback Sack, Scene #02
